,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:26:05.000Z","msg":"不身想話樓主戇鳩鳩印度都吹奏<br />\n<br />\n但諗一諗其實敵人既敵人就係朋友<br />\n<br />\nG持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:48:55.000Z","msg":"香港保衛戰中，香港守軍包括兩營印度部隊 : 第7拉吉普團第5營及第14旁遮普團第2營。<br />\n<br />\n城門碉堡失陷後，大陸旅開始撤回港島。兩營印軍連續兩日於九龍山脊行軍，再到無陸路可退的魔鬼山佈防，聯同於九龍城登艦到山上設立總部的大陸旅旅長華里士准將等指揮人員，成為九龍留守到最後的部隊。日軍第229聯隊來犯，英軍於馬游塘防線接戰。印軍表現英勇，曾經擊退日軍攻勢 。－<a href=\"http://fb.com/203212896680153\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2F203212896680153&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbgxjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=f24fbf66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.com/203212896680153</a>"},{"pid":"891db490ef7f54ed7cbf06670e416131013db7cc","tid":1475832,"uid":278133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7afee7ffdeff7457419d9c766610eed9d6f9f3c2","tid":1475832,"uid":276382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7b2e8fe44b87fdfd2e280d51d80dc797eb460b2","tid":1475832,"uid":278133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:34:37.000Z","msg":"邊到有得買美國國旗?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:48:18.000Z","msg":"淘寶/維城士多/中環石板街/油麻地國旗舖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bc8f5b92fcce42e6e1c4f1207d2d6c4a76d9af","tid":1475832,"uid":99442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6b182f2a19cb46d1f50a76e71002dbd95347826","tid":1475832,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b861b2199655f1d95cfa8ae754e8dcf721e2e37","tid":1475832,"uid":99442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b82a16759863266405655a35f94b1ad2ba4839cc","tid":1475832,"uid":269681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:18:26.000Z","msg":"8月24有荃葵遊行 身為青衣友一定要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係作為歴史人又想黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:19:17.000Z","msg":"時間上會唔會可以夾到?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:23:33.000Z