\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5555565cfe311718fc1b9a5ff5a106f0622f29d7","tid":1475832,"uid":226569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:17:44.000Z","msg":"【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n// The UK should give Hong Kong citizens full UK nationality as a means of reassurance amid the current standoff with Beijing, the chair of the influential Commons foreign affairs committee has argued. (The Guardian)//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅take返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打000000 或 N/A<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbgxjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=2e322721\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"f5c9e0f109a58961c9b19604592850161a179147","tid":1475832,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:22:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77d92b73919c4480a0e3babee8b7e6b75134cb6c","tid":1475832,"uid":107478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DMh70kj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDMh70kj.jpg&h=2feb58bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PcjRHyE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPcjRHyE.jpg&h=932bd70a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n齊來參與instagram同facebook嘅 #全城㩒美元 #USDchallenge 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l4FGKy0Nbz4Vdug